 rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/guillermo-del-toro-once-planned-to-direct-a-star-wars-film-3502345">吉尔莫·德尔·托罗曾计划执导一部《星球大战》电影</a>后，首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上出现。</p> ;
