l="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-suga-enlists-in-the-military-see-you-all-in-2025-3502333">BTS 的 Suga 入伍后的帖子：“See you all in 2025”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
